name: Comit Developers
tag_list: marketing, hosting, web-development, we-design, seo, search-engine-marketing, magento, wordpres
overview:
Founded in 2011, Comit Developers is the product of a successful merger between ET Developers and Comit Technologies.

Gerlad Miguez and Spencer Hoyt have combined their passion for usable, search engine friendly websites, and high quality, attractive design, to create a powerhouse of innovation.

Comit Developers provides a wide range of services spanning from website development and hosting, to internet marketing.

They service large eCommerce sites, as well as small Mom & Pop companies, and can tailor a custom solution for an organization of any size.
